hostname -i
ip addr show
/sbin/ifconfig eth0


Try searching for them:

find / -name ifconfig 2>/dev/null

If they're there then just update your path variable:

export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/sbin:/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/local/games:/usr/game


